wikipedia_page.main: Marie-José Villiers, Lady Villiers (30 April 1916 – 1 February 2015) was a British-born Belgian countess, born Countess Marie-José de la Barre d’Erquelinnes who worked as a British spy during World War II.

response: *Marie-José Villiers, 98, British-born Belgian World War II spy and countess.Marie-José Villiers Belgian Resistance agent who escaped the close attentions of the Gestapo and transmitted valuable information to Britain
